- The results are ordered by the total transaction value in descending order.

- Market trends represent the fluctuation in prices over time;
- Revenue per trend is calculated by dividing the total revenue from transactions by the number of market trend entries;
- This metric helps in understanding the profitability of crops in relation to market dynamics.

